Two graphs G and H have the following adjacency matrices:

G =  \begin{bmatrix} 
 0 & 1 & 0 \\
 1 & 0 & 1 \\
 0 & 1 & 0 \\
\end{bmatrix}

H = \begin{bmatrix} 
 0 & 1 & 1 \\
 1 & 0 & 1 \\
 1 & 1 & 0 \\
\end{bmatrix}

Are G and H isomorphic? If they are, provide an isomorphism between the two graphs. If they are not, explain why not.
